; Coverage for history.cc: direct (forward) price lookup ($ to EUR)

commodity $
    note US Dollar
    format $1,000.00

commodity EUR
    format 1,000.00 EUR

P 2024/01/01 $ 0.92 EUR

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --market -X EUR
          -92.00 EUR  Assets:Cash
           92.00 EUR  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
